    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Unconditional written promises to pay on demand, or at a fixed or determined future time, a certain sum of money to, or to the order of, a specified person or to the bearer.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
